T1  - The Interplay Between Forward-Looking Measures and Target Setting
AU  - Bouwens, Jan
AU  - Kroos, Peter
Y1  - 2016/07/19
PY  - 2016
DA  - 2017/09/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2016.2481
